       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=EQII%20Rep%20Comments%20on%20Secondary%20Markets&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Fnews%2FEQII%2Fnews_37.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
